subject: Basketball
College Athletics
NCAA Basketball Tournament
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kia Vaughn of Rutgers is considered one of the best centers at any college. She will lead her teammates Sunday night against East Carolina in the first round of the N.C.A.A. tournament.
